data.description: Lovely home on a beautiful lot, featuring tidy landscaping and private yard backing up to pond! Foyer welcomes, with coat closet and attached garage access. Large kitchen offers butcher block storage island, modern fixtures, and pantry; new refrigerator and dishwasher. Living room with floor to ceiling windows for excellent natural light, gas fireplace (NRTC) and chandelier. Formal dining room. Window lined sunroom/family room with vaulted ceiling steps out to stamped concrete patio. Primary suite boasts expansive walk in closet and en-suite bath with double sinks and tub shower. Two additional bedrooms and full bath! Full basement with poured foundation, washer and dryer, and sump pump. Updates include roof (2019) and new furnace/AC (2020). Enjoy this bright, modern feel and fantastic, serene outdoor spaces!
